<!--MOVEMENT ORDERS TABLES GO HERE-->
	<table border=0 cellpadding=10 cellspacing=0 width=100%>
	<tr><td class=bodycopy>

<ol>
<li>The normal rules of Diplomacy apply except as amended below.
<P><li>Russia and Turkey are not played.
<p><li>Rumania, Ukraine, Sevastopol, Moscow, and all spaces in Turkey 
	are impassable.
<P><li>St. Petersburg is no longer a supply center.
<P><li>The Aegean Sea extends through the Bosphorous, so that it is
	adjacent to the Black Sea.
<p><li>Warsaw becomes a neutral supply center and is renamed Poland.
<p><li>Victory is achieved through ownership of fourteen supply centers.
		<!--BODYCOPY ENDS HERE-->
	</td>
	</tr>
	</table>
	
</td>
</tr>
